<p>6、<a href="https://zh.ifixit.com/News/42949/apple-arm-and-what-it-means">苹果更换 ARM 芯片的解读</a>（英文）</p>
<p><img src="https://www.wangbase.com/blogimg/asset/202008/bg2020080311.jpg" alt="" title="" /></p>
